liked_videos.Title: Best Air Fryer Banana Bread #bananabread #bananabreadrecipe #airfryerrecipes #homemaking #homemade
liked_videos.Description:
Air Fryer Banana Bread
Ingredients: 
- 1 Ripe Banana 
- 1 Egg
- 1/4c Milk (of choice)
- 1 tsp Vanilla Extract
- 2 tbsp Oil or Melted Butter
- 3/4c All Purpose Flour
- 1/2 tsp Baking Soda
- 2-3 tbsp Brown Sugar
- Strawberries, Blueberries, Walnuts, etc. (optional)

Directions:
- Mash Bananas
- Mix in wet ingredients 
- Mix in dry ingredients 
- Mix in berries or nuts (optional)
- Put in Air fryer at 300 degrees fahrenheit for 30 minutes 

(Depending on your air fryer & pan, time & temp may vary. So just keep an eye on it and test it with a toothpick to see if it comes out clean. This recipe fills 2 of these 5x3 loaf pans in this video that I got from Publix.)
